        <!-- Introduction -->
        <section class="mb-12">
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                <strong>Mumbai, India</strong> - Reliance Industries Ltd. (RIL) today reported its financial results for the first quarter of fiscal year 2026, ending June 30, 2025. The conglomerate posted its highest-ever quarterly consolidated EBITDA and Net Profit, signaling a robust start to the fiscal year. The performance was largely driven by strong momentum in its consumer-facing businesses, Jio and Retail, alongside a significant one-time gain from the sale of investments.
            </p>
        </section>

